  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a large paella pan or skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the mussels and sea bass, skin side down, and cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the onion and garlic and cook for another 2 minutes.",
    "Add the chickpeas, smoked paprika, salt, and black pepper, and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the rice and orange juice, and stir to combine.",
    "Bring to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, for 20 minutes.",
    "Remove the lid and cook for an additional 10 minutes, or until the rice is tender and lightly toasted.",
    "Remove from the heat and let rest for 5 minutes before serving.",
    "Garnish with chopped parsley and serve immediately."
